  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they help a lot because they want to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's normal.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jewish Police and-- and the money was his picture.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You got the ghetto money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In a time like that, nobody thinks about the other one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody is selfish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even you-- you wasn't selfish, you get selfish because they want to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We get to-- we make theaters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- and we got a lot of songs about Rumkowski.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- we were-- even concentration camp, we came home after work, and we got a show in-- in the hall with the Hungarian girls and with-- they teach us Hungarian songs.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes you have to forget.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, we got a lot of shows in the ghetto what we made from--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, oh yes, and songs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of songs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have a song-- [SINGING IN YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's when the Jews-- when Moses took the Jews and they have only cream of wheat to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we have a song, [SINGING IN YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was thinking, very long, to make a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was-- he was thinking day and night to make the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SINGING IN YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he giving [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] is what they give the Jews when they passed the-- the-- the Red Ocean.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's all what they got is cream of wheat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we made everything songs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We got a lot of songs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we-- we-- we went to the theater and we've got the-- the-- the--- Russian a little bit sugar-- I don't know what they get.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to the theater with-- with everything It was-- for us, we got so used to it, it was normal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, for five years you have-- you have to do something.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
